{
  "stem": "25178.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So he was just going to work, that's what he thought he was going to do.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they told him also in a letter to bring warm clothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was 12.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother was 18, and he was in, in that preventorium.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he wasn't there when this happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was still dark, it was around 5 o'clock in the morning, and somebody knocked on the door.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother opened the door and we heard the voice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was actually-- it was a Belgian policeman who came knocking on the door and-- to tell us to pack and assemble in the street.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother must have known this was going to eventually happen because she had our suitcases packed already.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was ready.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All she had to do was get dressed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she dressed me, and we took the suitcases and we went onto the street.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And the whole street-- it was a whole Jewish neighborhood, so we had all the people standing outside in front of their homes with their suitcases.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And they called out their names.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the Germans, as meticulous as they tried to be, they called the names off in alphabetical order.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And every time they called off a name, those people, they were ordered to go into a truck.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And of course my name being Voorzanger, with a V, I was one of the last ones in the last truck.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my mother and I, we went into the truck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when the truck started to roll-- it was rolling very slowly-- my mother told me to jump.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And I didn't want to jump.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
